> Do you love ice cream, but want to be mindful about what you eat? We. Feel. You! Created with your favorite classic sundae flavors in mind, these pops and bites are entirely plant based, 100 calories or less per serving, only 4 grams of sugar, and infused with superfoods like lion's mane mushrooms. They're coconut milk–based with a roster of amazing flavors. They're an ice cream lover's dream come true.

Enjoy @Dream Pops Birthday Cake Crunch Bites{2%unit}.

